NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Now, lets talk about how the auction might go if I open 2C. On virtually all hands, responder bids 2D. The only exception is if responder has a 5+ card suit with 2 of the top 3 honors. Then he is allowed to bid the suit. So, theoretically, Kia can bid 3D over 2C. However, I don't like that bid because it takes up too much room. It is the same reason I am reluctant to open 2C when I have a good diamond suit. Because, the auction goes 2C-2D-3D, and we have preempted ourselves, at the 3D level with our first real bid. Let us see how would it have been if I was the dealer.|
